# ESP32 Power Monitor Project

## üîß Overview
This project monitors electrical power using an ESP32 and the PZEM004Tv30 module. It also hosts a web dashboard via SPIFFS to display live data and control relays.

## üß∞ Components Used
- ESP32-WROOM-32
- PZEM004T v3.0
- ESPAsyncWebServer
- HTML5 + JavaScript (for dashboard)
- Relay module

## üõ†Ô∏è Features
- Real-time Voltage, Current, Power monitoring
- Load ON/OFF control via web
- Total ON-time tracking
- Hysteresis logic for automatic control
- Hosted web dashboard (served from SPIFFS)
